    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>African cylindrical or biconical beads made of a type of reddish brown stone after which they are named, made by the Yoruba, particularly in Ilorin, Nigeria. They are no longer made though they are still used.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000045627/Sciama and Eicher, Beads and Bead Makers (1998)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cuentas africanas cilíndricas o bicónicas hechas de un tipo de piedra café-rojiza de las cuales toman su nombre, hechas por los Yoruba, particularmente en Ilorin, Nigeria. Aunque ya no se fabrican aún son usadas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Afrikaanse cilindervormige en dubbelkonische kralen, gemaakt van de roodachtig bruine steensoort waarnaar ze zijn vernoemd. Gemaakt door de Yoruba, voornamelijk in Ilorin, Nigeria. Ze worden niet meer gemaakt, maar nog wel gebruikt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
